# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
num_x, num_y denote the total numbers that can be filled while moving horizontally or vertically in a given row or column.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(N) where N = mn;
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: O(N) for creating the spiral matrix;
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

# Code
